Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷風 還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎瑪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼風先遣隊 已到達行星九號軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.38,0:07:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先遣隊在後續部隊到達前消滅接近谷風機和紬的奇居子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:07:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別讓奇居子靠近谷風機和紬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這麼多 沒完沒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.11,0:08:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別叫苦了 一定要保護好他們！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艦長 我要申報由隼風執行的奇居子掃蕩作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將谷風機他們作為誘餌 讓大群奇居子集中到地表一處
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫髮無傷地拿下行星九號
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把谷風他們當作誘餌？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這只是出於戰術需要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以 你試試
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誘餌被幹掉就前功盡棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.25,0:09:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要保護好他們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會讓他們平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二批後續部隊已到達
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三批 第四批也將很快會合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到達的機體迅速展開攻擊隊形
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動用全部火力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼風組成的奇居子討伐隊 全部到達軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發動總攻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掃蕩牠們 一隻也別放過！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各機確認自己負責的區域 別重疊了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.22,0:09:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人本體剩餘100隻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,焰 往你那裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙…竄來竄去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩餘90隻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩餘80隻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩餘70隻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩餘60隻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩餘50隻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩餘40隻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩餘30隻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩餘20隻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:11.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就差一口氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認最後一隻奇居子已泡狀分解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵奇居子剩餘本體0隻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經全部殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贏了啊…面對那麼多的奇居子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是換成以前 簡直是不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經控制住行星九號
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.58,0:10:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這場掃蕩戰打得非常漂亮 綠川司令助理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒事了 紬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊 伊札那呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這呢 紬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 都是多虧了紬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你來救我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.47,0:11:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能以那種狀態回希德尼婭來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.24,0:11:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭盔和操縱服都連備用的一起報銷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒法在保障駕駛員安全的同時排出那東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去從未有過被切離本體的胞衣自行攻擊人類的事例
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:11:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個胞衣看上去也不太危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷風 你能抱著紬飛上來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.31,0:12:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我試試
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這什麼姿勢…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.29,0:12:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我會不會很重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 紬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒擔心谷風會忍不住非禮胞衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼想 莎瑪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:12:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全機 準備歸航
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星白…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:41.00,eyecatch,NTP,994,0,0,,希德尼婭百景　隼風起降船塢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:44.01,eyecatch,NTP,923,0,0,,希德尼婭百景　落合舊地下研究設施內溫室
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.44,0:13:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功進入行星九號的衛星軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大眾合船的情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無變化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下算是告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:13:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過既然來到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就沒有退路了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.93,0:14:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}本日 希德尼婭成功進入了行星九號的軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}行星九號擁有豐富的資源
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}外圍星環是易守難攻的天然要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}司令部表示
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.36,0:14:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我們就此獲得了在必將到來的與大眾合船的戰鬥中極其重要的陣地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不能回頭了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.58,0:14:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再過不久 一百年前沒能實現的夢想就要成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的 轉生為究極生物的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷風長道 因你在佔領行星九號的戰役中功勳卓著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現授予你八機掌位勳章
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你成為騎士了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.24,0:15:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 不勝感激
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多 多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.89,0:15:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說谷風 把勳章給我看看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 煉 你也太不拿自己當外人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,焰你別管我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.02,0:15:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你 谷風長道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岐神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待你今後的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要向你道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你救了紬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岐神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.91,0:15:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星白…啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個胞衣怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前作為貴重的標本保存起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為重要的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.76,0:16:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…需要有冗餘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,授勳是早已被遺忘的制度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過用來激勵士氣倒似乎是上上之策啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小林！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別再利用那孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類的心是脆弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有英雄的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要撐過漫長的戰爭是多麼艱難
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你 應該都十分清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小林…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你在那幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你是…谷風操縱士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.30,0:17:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通行許可證
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 是要回老家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.14,0:17:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 這袋米
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.99,0:18:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請帶上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝 謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}長道看好 不要上去 by 廣樹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 沒聽您的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 我很慶幸自己離開了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經歷了許多事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變得越來越喜歡希德尼婭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了 爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還得到了這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.51,0:19:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好看著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.41,0:19:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我教你怎麼和奇居子戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,0:20:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.28,0:20:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.29,0:20:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去駕駛繼衛
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（S1-OP）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇604 已通過第一警戒線
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距離18萬千單位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西隊12部執勤機 抓緊準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.23,0:20:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來將開始討伐奇604
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.47,0:20:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛人隊各機 依次出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.05,0:23:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷風班 四機掌位
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.37,0:23:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.95,0:23:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.97,0:23:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望您能暫時替我保管一下 爺爺
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（END）
